    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_3_3041-3056",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3041-3056",
      "markText": "相信奇迹的人必然活在奇迹之中！",
      "totalCount": 1216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3041&rangeEnd=3056",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3041&rangeEnd=3056"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_11_6686-6760",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6686-6760",
      "markText": "当你在别人身上发现了什么你不喜欢的东西时，就是在自己内在也有那个东西，你的任务就是清理它。当你清理干净时，它也会离开别人。事实上，它会离开这个世界。",
      "totalCount": 1173,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6686&rangeEnd=6760",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=6686&rangeEnd=6760"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_19_2618-2703",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2618-2703",
      "markText": "爱所有一切。当你爱上它们，就会发生变化。吸烟只在你认为它有害时才有害；汉堡只在你认为它不健康时才不健康。夏威夷的古老传统认为，所有的一切都是源于思想，爱是最伟大的治疗师。",
      "totalCount": 1080,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2618&rangeEnd=2703",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2618&rangeEnd=2703"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_9_1400-1466",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1400-1466",
      "markText": "对自己的生命完全负责意味着，在你生命中的每件事——只因为它们发生在你生命里——都该你负责。从某种程度上说，这整个世界都是你创造的。”",
      "totalCount": 1020,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1400&rangeEnd=1466",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1400&rangeEnd=1466"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_7_4962-5042",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4962-5042",
      "markText": "比如有个很有启发性的声明：“‘荷欧波诺波诺’大我意识视每个问题为机会而非磨难。问题不过是旧有记忆的重现，是为了再给我们一次机会，用爱的眼光去看、以灵感去行动。”",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4962&rangeEnd=5042",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4962&rangeEnd=5042"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_10_6566-6602",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6566-6602",
      "markText": "如果你从零极限的零状态出发，你根本不需要意图，你只需接收并付诸行动即可。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6566&rangeEnd=6602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6566&rangeEnd=6602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_6_3485-3548",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3485-3548",
      "markText": "每个人都有在1月1日下定决心，在1月2日就忘得一干二净的经历。虽然意愿都很好，但是深层的某些东西并没有和意识上的欲望达成一致。",
      "totalCount": 795,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300039393&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3485&rangeEnd=3548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/da532e20813ab75e3g013f94?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3485&rangeEnd=3548"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300039393_3_4776-4826",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4776-4826",
